room_title: Escape room "Sherlock's Unsolved Mystery" by Sherlock's Escape Rooms in Florence (KY)
room_address: 40 Martha Layne Collins Blvd. Cold Spring, KY 41076
room_description: While investigating his last case, Sherlock Holmes, the greatest detective of all time, has gone missing.  Was it revenge? Jealousy?  Was his conniving brother, Mycroft in on it? Or was it his genius sister, Eurus?  Uncover the evidence, solve the mystery, and report back to Scotland Yard in an hour.
